    <string name="install_mod_zip_help_title">模组压缩包结构</string>

    <string name="install_mod_zip_help_message">
        ✅ 正确示例：\n\n
        单个模组：\n
        ModName/\n
        \u00A0\u00A0mod.info\n
        \u00A0\u00A0media/\n
        \u00A0\u00A0scripts/\n\n
        单个 ZIP 中包含多个模组：\n
        ModA/\n
        \u00A0\u00A0mod.info\n
        ModB/\n
        \u00A0\u00A0mod.info\n\n
        ❌ 错误示例：\n\n
        多余的外层文件夹：\n
        Downloads/\n
        \u00A0\u00A0ModName/\n
        \u00A0\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0mod.info\n\n
        缺少模组根目录：\n
        media/\n
        scripts/\n
        （根目录无 mod.info）
    </string>


